        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Botf lies are perhaps the most disgusting vermin native to the Expanse. Explorers tell sickening tales of removing maggots from living hosts\u2014or worse, comrades eaten alive by larvae. Once a botf ly finds a warm-blooded host, it uses its proboscis to insert eggs into the host\u2019s f lesh. When the eggs hatch, the larvae feed upon the host until they mature into adult f lies and exit."
        }
    ],
